Ask HN: Are You Wearing Sunscreen?
text:
I'm seeing a lot of opinions recently on HN about sunscreen, so I'm looking to poll the community on the topic.

For context - I'm living in socal, I'm cycling 70-100 miles for at least one day, 20-40 other days with at least one rest day, and some days past 12PM (70-100 mile days).

For those who are in the sun for extended periods - are you wearing sunscreen? If so, what are you using? If not, any helpful strategies? Thanks everyone for your advice.

This email really freak me out
text:
Context: https://ibb.co/WgQ7WXH

A machine-learning company named Qdrant recently sends me a promotional email (as attached on screenshot)

this, really freak me out!!!!!

- the email address that they're send are never being on the same account where my real name belongs

- the email address that they're send are never registered on my private github account (with m real name), I have 2 github account (company & private), both of them are unrelated

- they marketing data are based on my github stars? wth?

"Relation" of my data https://ibb.co/MRXnK3B

I come to ask directly to the person who sends me the email, and they're just replying with:

- what is your email?

- you are not into machine learning?

really no idea how they got my real & well-connected data, any suggestion to prevent this on future?
